{"tid":35993,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"[女人揸車] 各位司機大哥 路面問題求教","createTime":"2016-12-12T12:08:41.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-12T15:08:18.000Z","uid":63392,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0a385f3c813c702dbbd0280145bbd98ee85aea2e","tid":35993,"uid":63392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T12:08:41.000Z","msg":"各位司機大哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你地平時揸車嗰陣有冇留意到邊啲路/邊條街嘅標示綫甩哂色/矇到睇唔到？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n即係箭嘴、雙黃綫、讓路綫、影斜綫嗰啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n會唔會因為咁而唔知應該轉邊？<br />\n或者甚至試過因為咁而爭啲出事？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n小女唔係諗住學車 亦唔識揸車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但想了解下有冇呢啲情況發生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大家分享下，有錯請指點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e5d5e1d945a43a6574a54fddc701a604cbd3886","tid":35993,"uid":63392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T14:10:18.000Z","msg":"推推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40a238d15b596918d5b822c194cb89ade05e4660","tid":35993,"uid":24284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T14:12:29.000Z","msg":"女人唔好渣車，唔該<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d674691918e7639b52bf6de67138ba677451a4c1","tid":35993,"uid":63392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T14:31:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>女人唔好渣車，唔該<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔會啊 自己都唔想遺禍人間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係想問下你地有冇試過遇過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n分享下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"835432cd14bf64e587240a649554d9a473c3b6e0","tid":35993,"uid":12303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T14:35:10.000Z","msg":"熟路咪自然無呢個問題<br />\n<br />\n*香港其實好細"},{"pid":"d36fb03a9e1eb263390333d8af2dd123e12232e6","tid":35993,"uid":61741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T15:08:18.000Z","msg":"睇燈既角度、睇牌，睇糕筒<br />\n好多野設計出黎都有諗過。<br />\n就算地下條線無色都應該要睇其他野"}]}